中國指控係美軍所為，而令到trump同中國應該以後無計傾<br />\ncash out救國之餘都一蚊都唔會放係美國，報復式急跌<br />\n如果見到呢個大picture，好自然會諗低位就係09年中資入巿位，仲未計連鎖反應 <br />\n<br />\n全球跌巿反為中國股巿無乜影響? 政治巿之外因為就係cashout 的錢回流托住，如果連香港都cash out，即係香港都係一隻棄子，中國唔想再用香港股巿做跳板去跟國際秩序 (由趕記者果一下就知中共做左決定) <br />\n<br />\n咁cashout法好有打仗前味道，而家港股中資退場，美國會唔會入黎接貨做莊 ? 而家應該唔會，因為香港under中共，美國培育星加玻取代香港"},{"pid":"850d054a82643b71194ae4b4f16560251ea721a6","tid":1939874,"uid":52684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T23:11:56.000Z","msg":"比較驚佢20000係底 炒唔到底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8781e1fb1d55f30f9078ca082caedf8aa00c1080","tid":1939874,"uid":24989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T23:31:49.000Z","msg":"又出口術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97eae4d67307fdf172678f72eea3f6b16ade22f1","tid":1939874,"uid":91813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T23:36:18.000Z","msg":"大佬呀 呢10年印左幾多錢<br />\n之後10年無限QE又會印幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2cf103584cdc72181a3591c7665cb4036056cea","tid":1939874,"uid":61484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T23:39:49.000Z","msg":"只有0係底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c28d9d755f6da5232ed3a34c6ee337a4ab6d7ea","tid":1939874,"uid":316979,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"86bd46c687a12ab19e76f4d169a61f4bde36785e","tid":1939874,"uid":130438,"like":82,"dislike":5,"score":77,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T11:45:46.000Z","msg":"單野都未完<br />\n咁快入貨<br />\n笑死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T23:42:05.000Z","msg":"識好多人都分批入<br />\n因為你永遠冇可能知幾時出新藥<br />\n可能聽日可能下個月可能下年<br />\n有理想既價就入少少先"},{"pid":"59ea158703b121526752ffcf0bcfe9e2679b06b4","tid":1939874,"uid":106756,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ec4eee37caedd60409f3ac09ce756906630c8397","tid":1939874,"uid":30006,"like":17,"dislike":3,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTim